{"tid":841644,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［技能發動］屋企門口執到隻雀求收養","createTime":"2018-09-29T16:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T17:09:19.000Z","uid":75613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2c88f9d61b7d3d9a338d82f55d987ffcf0d57320","tid":841644,"uid":75613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"頭先返屋企嗰陣，見到門口有隻雀阻住我開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/000208_1075577014ff2736a82719fbdae2dea3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F000208_1075577014ff2736a82719fbdae2dea3.png&h=30ebaecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔肯定係咪走失定係棄養，佢好乖咁上咗手跟手入埋屋，同埋佢都飛得唔高，擔心佢就咁放返出去會死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/000517_fb994608110029248222fd200f89067a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F000517_fb994608110029248222fd200f89067a.png&h=d3f3e2b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/000936_4171410d307b4acf7640a9a42fcea8e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F000936_4171410d307b4acf7640a9a42fcea8e7.png&h=08f34a40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇黃大仙嘅巴絲走失左隻雀或者有心養嘅都希望可以儘快聯絡，屋企人唔鍾意自來雀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望好心人可以救佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/sodiumsan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsodiumsan&d=%2FYj1B1gVb%2BCtfA9wV4Zofp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=87b4674a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sodiumsan</a>"},{"pid":"dfc805d21da4b2945a795be2e4cba66d63d236da","tid":841644,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T16:15:09.000Z","msg":"相思"},{"pid":"f3b5c879f10d66d63934a6bad04167a